project_descr: Human Security Fund Pilot Project for Social Cohesion, Conflict Prevention, Violence Reduction and Human Security in Support to Youth of the Central African Republic

outputs.output_descr: The living conditions of 3,500 individuals (2,000 men and 1,500 women), including youths and other vulnerable groups, are improved through their engagement in diversified livelihoods and income-generation activities.
